1. *Ustao* sam rano jutros. (I got up early this morning.)
2. On je *ustao* i otišao na posao. (He got up and went to work.)
3. Kada se *ustao*, osetio je jak bol u leđima. (When he got up, he felt a strong pain in his back.)
4. Ustani *ustao* već jednom! (Get up, you've already slept enough!)
5. *Ustajanje* u ranim jutarnjim satima može biti teško za neke ljude. (Getting up in the early morning hours can be difficult for some people.)
6. Ja obično *ustajem* u šest sati ujutro. (I usually wake up at six in the morning.)
7. Većina ljudi *ustaje* iz kreveta sa desne strane. (Most people get out of bed on the right side.)
8. Kada sam *ustao*, video sam da je napolju padao sneg. (When I got up, I saw that it was snowing outside.)
9. *Ustajanje* rano može biti korisno za produktivnost. (Getting up early can be beneficial for productivity.)
10. Oni su *ustali* sa stolica kada sam ušao u sobu. (They got up from their chairs when I entered the room.)